data.name: TextAbout.Text
data.value:
This program can be used to change graphics on Scumm 5 and 6 games.
It was originally developed for internal use at ScummBR translation group, to allow our artists to translate the game that contains english texts.
Supports extraction and injection of: * Background Images (all codecs) * Background Z-Planes * Objects Images - including multiple images per object. * Objects Z-Planes - including multiples z-planes per image. * Costumes - All frames.
I wold like to say thank you to Jestar Jokin (http://www.jestarjokin.net/blog/category/scumm/) for his great help and for being so nice with me, provinding his source codes and pointing me to links where I could learn a lot about the scumm data and image formats. Without his help, this program never existed.
I also would like to say thanks to SCUMMVM, SCUMM REVISITED and SCUMMC sites for providing a lot of useful technical information on theirs sites. I made this tool based on what I learned there.
This program utilizes BE.HexEditor to display binary data. More information and download of the control on http://sourceforge.net/projects/hexbox/
